Usage: AesToolApp action inputfile mode key [iv]

Arguments:
 action     Specify e for encryption or d for decryption
 inputfile  File to be encrypted or decrypted
 mode       Block cipher mode of operation { CBC ECB}
 key        128 or 256 bit key in hex format 
            Example (128 bit): 00112233445566778899AABBCCDDEEFF

Options (ignored in ECB mode):
 iv         128 or 256 bit initialization vector in hex format
            Example (128 bit): 00112233445566778899AABBCCDDEEFF

